00077 /* file_in_zip_read_info_s contain internal information about a file in zipfile,
00078     when reading and decompress it */
00079 typedef struct {
00080     CHAR  *read_buffer;            /* internal buffer for compressed data */
00081     z_stream stream;               /* zLib stream structure for inflate */
00082 
00083     UINT32 pos_in_zipfile;         /* position in byte on the zipfile, for fseek*/
00084     UINT32 stream_initialised;     /* flag set if stream structure is initialised*/
00085 
00086     UINT32 offset_local_extrafield;/* offset of the local extra field */
00087     UINT  size_local_extrafield;   /* size of the local extra field */
00088     UINT32 pos_local_extrafield;   /* position in the local extra field in read*/
00089 
00090     UINT32 crc32;                   /* crc32 of all data uncompressed */
00091     UINT32 crc32_wait;              /* crc32 we must obtain after decompress all */
00092     UINT32 rest_read_compressed;    /* number of byte to be decompressed */
00093     UINT32 rest_read_uncompressed;  /*number of byte to be obtained after decomp*/
00094 
00095     BinData* jar_bin_data;
00096 
00097     UINT32 compression_method;      /* compression method (0==store) */
00098     UINT32 byte_before_the_zipfile; /* byte before the zipfile, (>0 for sfx)*/
00099 } BinDataInReadStatusInfo;
00100 
00101 typedef struct {
00102     BinData* jar_bin_data;      /* the binary data of the jar-file*/
00103     JarFileGlobalInfo gi;       /* public global information */
00104     UINT32 byte_before_the_zipfile;/* byte before the zipfile, (>0 for sfx)*/
00105     UINT32 num_file;             /* number of the current file in the zipfile*/
00106     UINT32 pos_in_central_dir;   /* pos of the current file in the central dir*/
00107     UINT32 current_file_ok;      /* flag about the usability of the current file*/
00108     UINT32 central_pos;          /* position of the beginning of the central dir*/
00109 
00110     UINT32 size_central_dir;     /* size of the central directory  */
00111     UINT32 offset_central_dir;   /* offset of start of central directory with
00112                                    respect to the starting disk number */
00113 
00114     FileInfo cur_file_info; /* public info about the current file in zip*/
00115     FileInfoInternal cur_file_info_internal; /* private info about it*/
00116     BinDataInReadStatusInfo* pfile_in_zip_read; /* structure about the current
00117                                         file if we are decompressing it */
00118 } JarBinDataStatusInfo;
